events.name: Almost got hit by a tree
events.details: There had been a heavy ice storm that day. The power flickered and it seemed like a tree branch might have hit the lines. I went out to see the state of the tree, i heard a loud snap, turned around, ran and jumped into the backdoor. Turns out a branch snapped and if the power lines weren't there it could have hit me
